import { Card, Col, Container, Row } from "react-bootstrap"

const Register=()=>{
    return(
        <>
            <Container>
                <Row>
                    <Col>
                        <Card>
                            <Card.Header className="mg-4">
                                Register
                            </Card.Header>
                            
                        </Card>
                    </Col>
                </Row>

            </Container>
        </>

    )
}
export default Register
